<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个暴风雨的晚上，有个魔法师敲门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>魔法师全身都湿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请让我躲躲雨吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆正在王座室里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卫兵把魔法师带了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是个魔法师，叫戴蒙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我能等到雨停再走吗？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然可以！”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在火边暖暖身体吧，戴蒙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我给你拿喝的。”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥动了魔杖。“水！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！一桶水出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>戴蒙大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不喜欢水。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想喝热饮料。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>戴蒙在火边烤干了衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多美丽的城堡啊！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我带你四处看看吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他带着戴蒙出去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我敢说，戴蒙一定没弄错过咒语。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪皱起了眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不相信那个魔法师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要跟着他们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王给戴蒙介绍了恐怖地牢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地牢里又黑又湿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天花板不停地滴水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有人能从这里逃出去！”国王自豪地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，戴蒙挥动了魔杖。噗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王被关进了地牢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>戴蒙大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，你也逃不出去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我来管理这儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
